nodes.text: Star Wars: Build Your Own R2-D2 93

Star Wars: Build Your Own R2-D2 93 is the ninety-third issue of the Star Wars: Build Your Own R2-D2 published by De Agostini. It came with mountings for the electrics of the buildable R2-D2 and contained the articles "Picture-Perfect Planets", "R2-D2 Astromech Part 14" and "Giants of Industrial Robotics".
